{"tid":532600,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"女教師の誘惑　正到讓人興奮高潮","createTime":"2018-01-18T04:01:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T05:01:42.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"45fb0e6c31448acd96976ead1461988cc3e179d6","tid":532600,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:01:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180118/640_489de2d431290495ef6b85b2cd1f5e6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180118%2F640_489de2d431290495ef6b85b2cd1f5e6e.jpg&h=7e0f2bf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泰國女教師の誘惑，正到讓人興奮高潮。<br />\n<br />\n本月16日是泰國的教師節，休假一天，泰國軍政府總理帕若育除了祝泰國老師們教師節快樂，也希望老師遵守著「好老師、好信念」的本分教育學生，而泰國鄉民們更蒐羅全國最正老師，希望激起大家的「學習慾望」，也慶祝教師節快樂。<br />\n<br />\n另據《泰北網》報導，在泰國社會中，教師的地位相當崇高，在6月還有一個「拜師節」，泰國已故國王蒲美蓬更曾說：「老師是一種很特殊的職業，沒辦法讓人升官發財，可是卻可以讓人得到心靈的富足。」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"8f0d04989e7df46ca017898dc2215fa09e48da7c","tid":532600,"uid":157193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:02:49.000Z","msg":"喺咪真女人嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e531f8abca1332423788d98dbcb4d62cf2a57bc7","tid":532600,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f0d04989e7df46ca017898dc2215fa09e48da7c","tid":532600,"uid":157193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:02:49.000Z","msg":"喺咪真女人嚟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T04:48:23.000Z","msg":"個內心係真女人"},{"pid":"ffc1c7d670e876d21f88b418aa29f220b2a661f9","tid":532600,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e531f8abca1332423788d98dbcb4